text: Sean Charles O'Keefe (born January 27, 1956) is an American politician. He is the former chairman of Airbus Group, Inc.,"EADS taps government vet", politico.com, October 22, 2009; accessed September 18, 2014. former Secretary of the Navy, former Administrator of NASA, and former chancellor of Louisiana State University (LSU).History of LSU, Louisiana State University, January 15, 2010 He is a former member of the board of directors of DuPont. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:United States Secretaries of the Navy Category:Administrators of NASA Category:Businesspeople from New Orleans Category:Politicians from New Orleans
